Ques : Two identical trains at the equator start travelling round the world in opposite direction. They start together , run at the same speed and are on different tracks. Which train will wear out its wheel treads first?

Solution : Train tarvelling against the spin of the earth will whear out its wheel first because there will be less centrifugal fornce acting on it.  

To know more about centripetal and centrifugal forces.
